  <answerContent><![CDATA[<h3>To make a booking over the phone</h3>
<p>Our best prices are always available online. However, should you require further information before you book, or would like to book one of the few holidays that are not available online, our UK based sales team will be happy to help you.</p>
<p><strong>You can call them on: </strong><span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111.</span></p>
<h3>Opening hours:</h3>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Monday - Friday: </strong>9am - 6:00pm</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Saturday</strong>: 9am – 5:30pm</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Sunday</strong>: Closed</p>
<p>You can use the live chat on our website or email <a href="mailto:enquiries@inghams.co.uk">enquiries@inghams.co.uk</a> and we will endeavour to reply to your enquiry as soon as possible.</p>
<h3>Help with your online booking</h3>
<p>If you are experiencing technical difficulties whilst booking online, you can use the live chat on our website or please contact our Reservations team on: <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111.</span></p>]]></answerContent>
